As we have noted the Microsoft products interact very well with
SQL Server.

Regarding the name Microsoft refers to its 'Microsoft SQL Server'
that is a RDBMS developed by Microsft 30 years ago.

It is a popular program for databases Management

This program is a RDBMS that uses T-SQL language.

You can download a version (the latest is the 2019's) directly
from Microsoft website
You can download the Express or the Developer version.

As the Developer version is the most complete one
download that.
